reviews.review_text:
Just like being there! This is the best recording dynamically of all the variants of this show, which I attended.  The balance between all the instruments, vocals and audience is just astounding.  It's one of the few recordings, including the two "store bought" releases of this stand, the last with Brent in Atlanta - that is TRULY like being there.  The hansokolow was the best, but this is even better!

Dunno know how you did it Sir Mick, but mega-kudos for this scintillating contribution to the community!
